  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Discover Slovenia by combining the contrasting resorts we feature. Combine the cultural city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/ljubljana" title="Ljubljana">Ljubljana</a><span> and enjoy the restaurants and great nightlife with a relaxing stay in the beautiful resort of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/lake-bled" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a><span> and visit the only island in </span><a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a><span>. Or head to the mountains and the wonderful resorts of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span> and Lake Bohinj. Kranjska Gora has stunning views towards the Julian Alps and the distant peaks of the Karavanke mountains. </span><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/lake-bohinj" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a><span> is famous for its crystal clear waters and is the source of the mighty River Sava. </span></p>
<div>
