<h2><a name="Tour highlights"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Tour highlights</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Tailor-made holiday to suit your wishes</li>
<li>Experience the natural beauty of Slovenia by visiting the lakes, mountains and countryside</li>
<li>Explore the friendly and cultural capital city of Ljubljana</li>
<li>Enjoy various activities like hiking or mountain biking</li>
<li>Simply relax in various beautiful locations and discover one of Europe's hidden gems</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-slovenia/discover-slovenia#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Itinerary"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Multi Centre Combinations</span></h2>
<p><strong>Lake Bled, Slovenia &amp; Kitzbühel, Austria</strong></p>
<p> 7 nights Lake Bled / 7 nights Kitzbühel</p>
<p>Please note: Transfers will be via Salzburg Airport and Slovenian resorts must be taken as the first centre.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Triglav National Park &amp; Ljubljana</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>All resorts can be combined for 3/4/7 days or longer ( Ljubljana, Bohinj , Bled)</li>
<li>All transfers will be direct between resorts except Ljubljana, which will operate via the airport</li>
<li>Transfers are included </li>
<li>Prices include flights, accommodation, transfer and meals as specified</li>
</ul>
<p>Shown are some of the most popular combinations, but other resorts and hotel combinations are also possible. Please call our reservations team on 01483 79 11 11 to book these holidays.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-slovenia/discover-slovenia#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Your holiday includes"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Your holiday includes</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Airport transfers</li>
<li>Meals as per hotel description </li>
</ul>
<p><span></span><strong>Your holiday excludes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Any extras, drinks, gratuities and personal expenses</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-slovenia/discover-slovenia#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Hotels"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Hotels</span></h2>
<p><strong>★★★★+ <a data-udi="umb://document/093bbc54785244aa9aa802856c0b18e8" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/lake-bled/grand-hotel-toplice" title="Grand Hotel Toplice">Grand Hotel Toplice</a>, Lake Bled</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ <a data-udi="umb://document/dcecccebd4fc4260b26e10a4cdbe9071" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/kitzbuhel/aktivhotel-schweizerhof" title="Hotel Schweizerhof">Hotel Schweizerhof</a>, Kitzbühel</strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ <a data-udi="umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora/best-western-hotel-kranjska-gora-formerly-hotel-lek" title="Best Western Hotel Kranjska Gora (formerly Hotel Lek)">Best Western Hotel</a><a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora/hotel-kompas" title="Hotel Kompas"></a>, Kranjska Gora </strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ <a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora/hotel-kompas" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas</a>, Kranjska Gora </strong></p>
<p><strong>★★★★ <a data-udi="umb://document/2aeb8216bf2947b9951b9a65f072cf51" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/lake-bohinj/hotel-jezero" title="Hotel Jezero">Hotel Jezero</a>, Lake Bohinj</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h2><a name="Departure dates"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Departure dates<a></a></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Saturday throughout the summer</li>
</ul>
